{"_path":"/tags/langs/sql","_dir":"langs","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"SQL","description":"SQL 语言广泛应用于各种关系数据库管理系统，如Microsoft SQL Server、MySQL、PostgreSQL、MariaDB和Oracle等。","name":"sql","icon":"devicon:azuresqldatabase","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"sql"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SQL"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"icon","props":{"className":["size-32"],"name":"devicon:azuresqldatabase"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SQL，全称 Structured Query Language，即结构化查询语言，是用于与关系数据库进行通信的标准语言。SQL 是关系数据库管理系统的核心，用于执行各种数据库操作，如数据定义、数据查询、数据更新、数据删除等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SQL 语言具有如下特点："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"综合统一"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SQL 能够处理数据库的定义、操作和控制，这意味着可以使用同一种语言来创建表结构、插入、查询、更新数据，以及设置访问权限和安全性控制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高度非过程化"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用户只需提出“做什么”，而无需指明“怎么做”，便可得到所需的信息。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"面向集合的操作方式"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SQL 采用集合操作方式，不仅查找结果可以是元组的集合，而且一次插入、删除、更新操作的对象也可以是元组的集合。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语言简洁，易学易用"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SQL 功能强大，但语言简洁，语法简单，好学好用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据统计方便直观"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SQL 提供了丰富的聚合函数，使得数据的统计和汇总变得方便和直观。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SQL 语句主要可以分为数据操作语言（DML）和数据定义语言（DDL）两大类。DML 用于查询和修改数据，包括 SELECT、INSERT、UPDATE 和 DELETE 等语句；DDL 则用于定义或改变表结构，如 CREATE、ALTER 和 DROP 等语句。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SQL 语言广泛应用于各种关系数据库管理系统，如 Microsoft SQL Server、MySQL、PostgreSQL、MariaDB 和 Oracle 等。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":5,"depth":5,"links":[{"id":"sql","depth":2,"text":"SQL"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:tags:langs:sql.md","_source":"content","_file":"tags/langs/sql.md","_extension":"md"}